cern.clhep
Class Units

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--cern.clhep.Units
public class Units
extends Object

High Energy Physics coherent system of Units. This class is a Java port of the C++ version found in CLHEP 1.4.0, which in turn has been provided by Geant4 (a simulation toolkit for HEP).

Version:
1.0, 09/24/99
